OL,3,CJury in Jeffrey Donaldson trial sent
OL,4,Chome for the day
OL,6,FThe jury in the sex offences trial of
OL,7,Fformer DUP leader Sir Jeffrey
OL,8,FDonaldson has been sent home for the
OL,9,Fday.
OL,11,FThe jury of five women and seven men
OL,12,Fat Newry Crown Court deliberated for
OL,13,Fthree hours and 10 minutes before
OL,14,FJudge Paul Ramsey sent them home. They
OL,15,Fwill resume deliberations on Friday.
OL,17,FThe 63-year-old former MP has pleaded
OL,18,Fnot guilty to 18 alleged offences.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/3
