OL,3,CJury in Jeffrey Donaldson trial sent
OL,4,Chome for the day
OL,6,FHis wife, Eleanor Donaldson denies
OL,7,Fseveral charges of aiding and abetting
OL,8,Fher husband's alleged offending.
OL,10,FShe is facing a trial of the facts on
OL,11,Fmental health grounds.
OL,13,FThe trial of the facts will test the
OL,14,Fevidence in the case but cannot result
OL,15,Fin a criminal conviction.
